OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784931509
OL,3,CSnatched, tortured and held for
OL,4,Cransom: Five men jailed over kidnapping
OL,6,FFive men have been jailed for
OL,7,Fkidnapping of a 21-year-old after he
OL,8,Fwas snatched from his home, locked in
OL,9,Fa storage unit, where he was violently
OL,10,Fassaulted and held for ransom.
OL,12,FShrewsbury Crown Court was told during
OL,13,Fthe two-day hearing that the five men
OL,14,Fcarried out the crime after
OL,15,Fdiscovering the victim, from Telford,
OL,16,Fwas in a relationship with a female
OL,17,Frelative of two of the kidnappers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
