PN,34502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784931509
OL,3,CSnatched, tortured and held for
OL,4,Cransom: Five men jailed over kidnapping
OL,6,FThe defendants, who had been lifelong
OL,7,Ffriends with the victim, did not
OL,8,Fapprove of his relationship with their
OL,9,Fadult relative so planned the kidnap,
OL,10,Fwith several failed attempts made
OL,11,Fthroughout December 2025.
OL,13,FThen, on Monday 29 December 2025 at
OL,14,Faround 2.18pm Jawad Hussain, Ehteshan
OL,15,FHussain, Shayyan Hussain and Faheem
OL,16,FChohan dragged the 21-year-old victim
OL,17,Ffrom his home in Arleston before
OL,18,Fputting him in the boot of a black
OL,19,FAudi A4.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784931509
OL,3,CSnatched, tortured and held for
OL,4,Cransom: Five men jailed over kidnapping
OL,6,FThey were handed a combined total of
OL,7,F37 years imprisonment for the
OL,8,Fkidnapping in December 2025.
OL,10,FCCTV then showed the vehicle leaving
OL,11,Fthe scene at speed, travelling through
OL,12,FWellington with the boot open and the
OL,13,Fvictim's feet hanging out of the car.
OL,15,FEventually the car stopped and Shayyan
OL,16,Fand Ehteshan got out and closed the
OL,17,Fboot before continuing their journey
OL,18,Fto a storage unit in Eyton.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
