CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784931509
OL,3,CSnatched, tortured and held for
OL,4,Cransom: Five men jailed over kidnapping
OL,6,FThe victim was then taken inside,
OL,7,Fwhere he was violently assaulted by
OL,8,Fhis kidnappers.
OL,10,FThe two vehicles then drove to
OL,11,FLilleshall Golf Club to dump the Audi,
OL,12,Fwith Shayyan getting into the
OL,13,FVolkswagen.
OL,15,FThe victim was left locked inside the
OL,16,Funit and tied to a chair.
OL,18,FThe abandoned Audi was reported to
OL,19,Fpolice with CCTV identifying the
OL,20,FVolkswagen as being involved and
OL,21,Fleading to Ali being identified.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
