PN,34505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784931509
OL,3,CSnatched, tortured and held for
OL,4,Cransom: Five men jailed over kidnapping
OL,6,FOfficers were able to locate and
OL,7,Farrest Ali on suspicion of kidnap at
OL,8,F4.53pm.
OL,10,FThe men then called the victim's
OL,11,Ffamily demanding money and threatening
OL,12,Fto kill him by throwing him off a
OL,13,Fbridge.
OL,15,FFollowing Ali's arrest, Ehteshan and
OL,16,FShayyan went back to the unit and put
OL,17,Fthe victim into a car driving him
OL,18,Ftowards north Shropshire.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784931509
OL,3,CSnatched, tortured and held for
OL,4,Cransom: Five men jailed over kidnapping
OL,6,FThen at 9.58pm police received a call
OL,7,Ffrom a takeaway in Whitchurch stating
OL,8,Fa man was claiming to have escaped
OL,9,Fkidnap and was seriously injured.
OL,11,FOfficers attended and identified him
OL,12,Fas the victim.
OL,14,FThe victim told officers that while
OL,15,FEhteshan and Shayyan were out of the
OL,16,Fcar, he was able to lock the doors and
OL,17,Fnoticing the keys in the ignition,
OL,18,Fdrive to safety.
OL,20,FHe was then taken to hospital for
OL,21,Ftreatment to his injuries.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784931509
OL,3,CSnatched, tortured and held for
OL,4,Cransom: Five men jailed over kidnapping
OL,6,FThe victim was also able to confirm
OL,7,Fthe identities of the four men, and
OL,8,Fofficers arrested Jawad, Ehteshan and
OL,9,FChohan, while Shayyan handed himself
OL,10,Finto police the following day.
OL,12,FJawad, Ehteshan, Chohan and Shayyan
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty to kidnap in January
OL,14,F2026.
OL,16,FAli pleaded not guilty to the charge
OL,17,Fbut was found guilty following a two-
OL,18,Fweek trial last month (June).
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
