PN,34508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784931509
OL,3,CSnatched, tortured and held for
OL,4,Cransom: Five men jailed over kidnapping
OL,6,FOn Wednesday and Thursday (23 July)
OL,7,Fthe defendants were given a combined
OL,8,Ftotal of 37 years in prison for the
OL,9,Fkidnapping:
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Lee
OL,12,FHolehouse said: "This was a horrifying
OL,13,Fordeal for the victim, who was
OL,14,Fkidnapped by men he had considered
OL,15,Ffriends for much of his life.
OL,26,@tD@QOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
