OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,346,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F345A1784931509
OL,3,CSnatched, tortured and held for
OL,4,Cransom: Five men jailed over kidnapping
OL,6,F"He was dragged from his home, held
OL,7,Fagainst his will, subjected to a
OL,8,Fviolent assault and threatened with
OL,9,Fdeath. The actions of these men were
OL,10,Fboth cruel and calculated, and the
OL,11,Fsentences handed to them reflect the
OL,12,Fseriousness of their offending.
OL,14,F"I would like to commend the victim
OL,15,Ffor the courage and resilience he has
OL,16,Fshown throughout this investigation
OL,17,Fand court process."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUyD@SO]
